                mistakes: [{ t: "LangChain as a black box", d: "Understanding what LangChain is doing underneath (the prompts, the retrieval call, the chain of requests) is essential for debugging and optimisation." }, { t: "No evaluation harness", d: "Building LLM applications without automated evaluation is building blind. Set up RAGAS or LangSmith evals before writing the first chain." }]
